subsect.p:
As well as the command descriptions in this document (especially the reference section ) you can get help for STILTS usage from the command itself. Typing
stilts -help
results in this output: &stilts-usage;

For help on the individual tasks, including their parameter lists, you can supply the word help after the task name, so for instance
stilts tcopy help
results in &tcopy-usage;

